Contains:

SISTERS AT WAR - The first volume. Repackaged version of Lo-Res Digital-TPB release.

DAUGHTERS OF STONE - Second volume. Repackaged Hi-Res Digital-TPB release. Each issue's last page(s) were revised for the TPB; the originals are included separately.

SHORTS - Seven shorter (4 to 12 pages) stories, originally published in the two "Origins" issues as well as in the form of TPB extras. Each story is bookended with appropriate pinup artwork - which worked out rather well here, if I do say so myself!

THE ART OF CARBON GREY - ~130 pages of concept art. Original Digital Lo-Res release.
